Automatic Easily create Slackware chroot jail for testing and
development SlackBuilds. Its for Slackware Stable and Current
64 bits only. Inspired by debootstrap.

Features:

* Create a completely clean Slackware 64 bits (stable/current)
  chroot environment.
* Select the Slackware series you want.
* Enter your new environment at any time by setting up the
  necessary special file (proc, dev, sys).
* Create a backup of your chroot environment to use at a later
  time.
